LICENSE — TBD

The OpenBand project has not yet finalized its licensing.

Current intent:
  • Documentation (this repository) — Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC-BY-4.0)
  • Source code (in a separate private repository)        — GNU AGPL v3.0

Until a formal LICENSE file is committed, the default is "all rights reserved."

If you need to reuse content from this repository before the license is
finalized, please open an issue or email the project owner. We intend for the
documentation to be widely shareable, but we cannot retroactively enforce
unstated terms.

This placeholder will be replaced with the final license text once the
legal review is complete.
